building on writing toward freedom politics and digital rights in africa this fiveweek social media outreach initiative will involve a curated dialogue on gvssafrica featuring five african language activists who will focus on the intersection of language and digital rights
identity matrix is funded by the africa digital rights fund of the collaboration on international ict policy for east and southern africa cipesa
