one traveler from spain who recently visited the dcma wrote on tripadvisor personally meeting the musicians was the best piece of my time on this island
as zanzibars tourism sector rapidly grows the dcma believes that music plays an essential role in the celebration preservation and promotion of swahili culture heritage and history
zanzibar is far more than its beaches and luxury hotels  its a place bursting with talent that stems from an extraordinary history of cultural connection and collaboration
