the first recorded cases of ebola occurred in 1976 near the ebola river in dr of congo
according to the centres for disease control and prevention cdc since then the ebola virus has emerged periodically from its natural reservoir which remains unknown to infect people in africa
ebola virus outbreaks since 1976
