a rumor about the spread of french yellow vest protests to other european countries went viral on chinese social media before christmas
the story emerged after french president emmanuel macron announced a number of concessions to address protesters grievances over economic policies
while macron expected calm and order be restored the chinesefabricated rumor predicted the opposite
multiple versions of the story were spread via a number of microblogging accounts on weibo and wechat quoting sources from a commodity wholesaler in yiwua city well known as a wholesaling centerwho stated that their entire stock of yellow vests in stock was sold out and more orders had been coming in from european nations such as sweden prague switzerland etc
the story implied that the yellow vest protests were spreading throughout the continent
